title: Ooltewah High School vs. Soddy Daisy High School
text: Share Updated: 10/03 12:50 am Soddy Daisy, TN (WDEF) - First quarter, Owls QB London Elrod throws to WR Kobe Jones, who almost takes it all the way in.Now it's 1st and goal, Owls RB Cameron Turner scores a touchdown.Score is 7 to O, Ooltewah on top.Bottom of the 2nd quarter got really exciting!Second and goal from the 2, Ooltewah's QB London Elrod hands to WR Rashun Freeman for a touchdown.Score is 16-0, Owls.Owl's QB London Elrod's pass is intercepted by Soddy DB Jacob Jordan.Now it's Soddy Daisy's turn!!!Trojan QB Justin Cooke hands off to RB Christian Bell for a touchdown.Score is 16-7, Ooltewah leads.Owl WR Scottie Strickland catches ball and touchdown!Score is 23-7, Owls.Now the play of the game!!!A 98-yard return by Soddy RB Christian Bell for a touchdown.Score is 23 to 14, Ooltewah still leads.Final score is 30 to 21, Ooltewah wins!
